w was conducted in Boston,\nMassachusetts, in July 2014. A link to Nan's full CV can be found at\n\\surlwww.hsph.harvard.edu/nan-laird/.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2015 05:53:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-14"}
