th the significant strengths are obtained in $E=10-15$ MeV. It is indicated\nthat the ISD excitations can be a good probe to experimentally search for new\ncluster states such as the $^{12}$C($1^-_2$) obtained in the present\ncalculation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2015 12:20:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
